ID Card Generator

ID Card Creator

This website is part of a non-commercial, volunteer-based project created by a student to enhance student safety during emergencies. It helps you generate a digital ID card containing vital information, including a scannable QR code. In critical situations, scanning this QR code can give first responders immediate access to emergency contacts, blood group, and essential identity details potentially saving lives.

Built using modern HTML5 and web technologies, this tool offers a fast, secure, and installation-free experience. Your data remains fully private and is never stored or transmitted. Everything is processed locally in your browser, no servers, no database, and no personal tracking.

Privacy first: All information disappears once the page is closed. Nothing is saved externally. You are entirely in control of your data.

ID Format: The ID card follows the industry-standard CR80 size (3.375 x 2.125 inches), ensuring it fits standard plastic ID card printers and holders.

For legal details, usage terms, and responsibilities, please read our Terms and Conditions.

🖨️ Printing Tips for Best Results:
  • Select “Actual size” or 100% scaling in the print dialog.
  • Don't select options like “Fit to page”, “Shrink to fit”, or "Fit to printable area".
  • Set margins to None or Minimum if available.
  • The generated ID card strictly follows the standard CR80 (3.375 x 2.125 inches).
  • Use good quality photo or card stock paper if possible.
